# Community Resources¬∂

Welcome! This page highlights resources built and maintained by the Agent Development Kit community.

Info

Google and the ADK team do not provide support for the content linked in these external community resources.

## Getting Started¬∂

[ Video Demo üì∫ Introducing Agent Development Kit A demo of building a multi-agent travel planner, showcasing core design principles. ](https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=zgrOwow_uTQ) [ Video üì∫ Getting started with Agent Development Kit Learn the fundamentals of agent definition and how to run and debug your first agent. ](https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=44C8u0CDtSo) [ Video üì∫ Getting Started with ADK Tools A guide to building a software bug assistant using tools like MCP and Google Search. ](https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=5ZmaWY7UX6k)
